        "message": "Patch Set 1: -Code-Review\n\nHi Jess.   The appc/deployment project doesn't contain anything for Sonar analysis.  The project was removed from the dashboard with ticket #44455 but the daily build was not updated accordingly.  Can we let this proceed?",
