        "timestamp": "2017-09-12 16:20:32.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Hi Jess.   The appc/deployment project doesn't contain anything for\n > Sonar analysis.  The project was removed from the dashboard with\n > ticket #44455 but the daily build was not updated accordingly.  Can\n > we let this proceed?\n\nI agree with skip, this job is just wasting LF, ONAP and ONAP member companies money. It provides no useful info in sonar. Why do we want it to continue to run? See https://sonar.onap.org/overview?id=38445",
